property.value: THE FORGE OF XSHATHRA IS AN EERIE PLACE. A TRADITIONAL PLACE OF WORSHIP TO THE PRINCE OF DARKNESS, IT IS NO SURPRISE THAT THOSE WHO SERVE DAL GURAK HAVE OCCUPIED IT. I WILL HAVE TO FIGHT MY WAY TO RECOVER THE HILT OF THE SWORD.

property.name: string-1
property.value: ENFIN, LE DERNIER FRAGMENT DE L'?P?E DE IANNA. AVEC ELLE, JE VAIS POUVOIR ENVOYER DAL GURAK EN ENFER UNE BONNE FOIS POUR TOUTES.

property.name: string-1-en
property.value: FINALLY, THE LAST FRAGMENT FROM THE SWORD OF IANNA. WITH IT, I WILL FINALLY BE ABLE TO SEND DAL GURAK TO HELL ONCE AND FOR ALL.

property.name: string-2
property.value: LE MOMENT EST VENU. VA AU TEMPLE DE IANNA, ET VOIS SI TU ES DIGNE DE BRANDIR SON ?P?E.

property.name: string-2-en
property.value: IT IS TIME. GO TO THE TEMPLE OF IANNA, AND SEE IF YOU DESERVE WIELDING HER SWORD.

property.name: string-3
property.value: AVEC CETTE HACHE, MES ENNEMIS VONT REJOINDRE L'ENFER QU'ILS N'AURAIENT JAMAIS D; QUITTER.

property.value: WITH THIS AXE MY ENEMIES WILL GO BACK TO THE HELL THEY SHOULD HAVE NEVER LEFT.

property.value: TU AS TROUV? LA COURONNE DU ROI D?MON. RAPPORTE-LA % SA PLACE.

property.name: string-4-en
property.value: THE CROWN THAT BELONGED TO THE DEMON KING MUST RETURN TO ITS PLACE.

property.name: string-5
property.value: JE POURRAI PASSER QUAND J'AURAI LE DERNIER FRAGMENT DE L'?P?E.

property.name: string-5-en
